{"tid":656353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：元朗旮旯","createTime":"2018-05-07T07:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T09:18:48.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"56321dbc1c3d7ed5c4b8c886ffdb10b7702c7e9e","tid":656353,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"輯相真係影完自己都覺得核突，但係間舖太細，又多人等，所以唔好意思比相機食太耐，就要急急開餐，希望大家多多包涵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間野都係啲文青打卡熱點黎，門口有啲陳設擺靚靚咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/152819_32ca910b38de5358c7a1f1565eae174a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F152819_32ca910b38de5358c7a1f1565eae174a.jpeg&h=e2139d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢個抹茶卷絕對唔係得個樣，基本上係喺香港食過數一數二嘅抹茶甜品黎。味道清新而冇澀味，微甜而冇膩感，最重要係唔會好似普通瑞士卷咁，蛋糕部分乾憎憎，食落口感比較係濕潤嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/153301_4ef006bd67084eb2081d4a21b69e6445.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F153301_4ef006bd67084eb2081d4a21b69e6445.jpeg&h=be37d25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥提沙丸子個樣同味道都普通，不過本身講明係麥提沙個餡，就好難有咩驚喜嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/153408_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F153408_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg&h=913088c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n杯加啡用金屬飲管係型啲，但我本身唔係環保撚黎，仲覺得好污漕......味道亦都係一般，不過30蚊唔駛都算係咁啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/153450_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F153450_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg&h=cddee73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外佢有個雞翼都幾好食，但係冇影到相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總括黎講價錢差唔多，食佢肯肯定好過食隔離B仔。"},{"pid":"226b89375ffa0ec574a6658fec5d4c38c17cd310","tid":656353,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},{"pid":"22dcef5f8219ba8b608fc8321729054cfd186d73","tid":656353,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"226b89375ffa0ec574a6658fec5d4c38c17cd310","tid":656353,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"話人須有理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4ebedd070c8685a18683c2b0217f98c032829a","tid":656353,"uid":27303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"好撚普通喎"},{"pid":"c42316d41ed11f6435342af6b62aee276a7e318e","tid":656353,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a4ebedd070c8685a18683c2b0217f98c032829a","tid":656353,"uid":27303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"好撚普通喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"只有抹茶卷幾好，其他非常普通"},{"pid":"dc1d828eaebaa2594231b3860dcfac087ba0c476","tid":656353,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"見到條鐵飲管已經想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd9794f005ae17ae0101f482ffac585ca52b5dc","tid":656353,"uid":828,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"上次食過 可一不可再<br />\n<br />\n個麥提莎米糍好細粒囉 個個打手都影到咁柒大粒<br />\n滿心歡喜去買外賣 38蚊9粒 麥提莎同個米糍都唔撚夾 皮還皮 麥提莎還麥提莎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/160326_c92db68fe2afde310c3f00c173761eea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F160326_c92db68fe2afde310c3f00c173761eea.png&h=5d225358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住試埋個鳩餅 佢話溝埋黑糖同煉奶一齊食<br />\n倒晒之後成pat屎咁 又軟lum lum <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/160331_23c6fc0e915819c6711b5e14517b3ce1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F160331_23c6fc0e915819c6711b5e14517b3ce1.png&h=3a2fd361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好失望 俾咗70蚊唔知食咗乜 唔好再吹奏了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44bcbddd407896271ab52e50d44b1adaeeff983","tid":656353,"uid":32227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"你啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c2b9380f4fb455fcec55feec5458e082a530b1","tid":656353,"uid":171786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8cd9794f005ae17ae0101f482ffac585ca52b5dc","tid":656353,"uid":828,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"上次食過 可一不可再<br />\n<br />\n個麥提莎米糍好細粒囉 個個打手都影到咁柒大粒<br />\n滿心歡喜去買外賣 38蚊9粒 麥提莎同個米糍都唔撚夾 皮還皮 麥提莎還麥提莎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/160326_c92db68fe2afde310c3f00c173761eea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=